creator: Sun Fire Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The brightest, fastest, and most handy LED Flashlight.

Flashlight is a totally free application that turns your smart phone into a super flashlight quickly and efficiently.

It has a strobe feature that makes the flash of your phone blink very fast and has super innovative themes.

Main features:
🌟 SOS: Built-in SOS signal.
🌟 Strobe: Strobe mode with 10 different frequencies.
🌟 Color Screen: Make your phone screen colorful.
🌟 Magnifying Glass: It can help you magnify small things.
🌟 Compass: It can help you point the way.
🌟 Morse: Send morse code in case of emergency.
🌟 Sound: Toggle the sound on or off.
🌟 Skin: Built-in 12 different color skins.
🌟 Shortcut: Create a shortcut on your phone screen.
🌟 Permission: No camera permission required.

With this app, you can do:
🏃 Walking in a dark place.
📙 Read a real book at night.
🔑 Find your keys in the dark.
👷 Save yourself while black out at night.
⛺ Light the way when camping and hiking.
🏠 Light your room during a power outage.
🎉 Make your party shining.
🔆 Illuminate the roads when Outdoor traveling.

This is the best Flashlight in the Play Store. Please try it!
